  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Omega-3 Fatty Acids(Omacor®) for the Treatment of Immunoglobulin A Nephropathy</brief_title>
  <acronym>IgAN</acronym>
  <official_title>Minimization, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Multi-center, Phase 3 Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Omega-3 Fatty Acids(Omacor®) for the Treatment of IgA Nephropathy</official_title>
