  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare omega-3 fatty acids with placebo for efficacy in
      retardation of increase of serum creatinine(SCr) in IgA Nephropathy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In the current clinical study, attempts are made to assess the safety and efficacy of omega-3
      fatty acids by comparing between omega-3 fatty acids and the placebo in Korean patients with
      IgA nephropathy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
